markdownRemark.html: The next JaxFusion meeting will be this coming Tuesday, August 7th at 6:30 pm. The meeting will be at Modis building in downtown Jacksonville. We will be going over some of the newest features of ColdFusion 8 which you may or may not heard about. I have a lot of giveaway items for this meeting.
